service: whalepay-backend

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  stage: ${opt:stage, 'dev'}
  region: ${opt:region, 'us-east-1'}
  environment:
    COINBASE_KEY_NAME: ${env:COINBASE_KEY_NAME}
    COINBASE_KEY_SECRET: ${env:COINBASE_KEY_SECRET}
  iam:
    role:
      statements:
        - Effect: Allow
          Action:
            - execute-api:Invoke
          Resource: "*"

functions:
  api:
    handler: src/lambda.handler
    events:
      - httpApi:
          path: /
          method: GET
      - httpApi:
          path: /api/{proxy+}
          method: ANY
    cors: true

# Using built-in esbuild
custom:
  build:
    esbuild:
      bundle: true
      minify: true
      sourcemap: true
      exclude: ['aws-sdk']
      target: 'node18'
      platform: 'node'
